task.summary: Added sendConfirmEmail method to send activation emails
Changed mongodb credentials to use mLab
Added file to generate python3.5 compatible package
Added generateConfirmCode method to generate random 6 digit confirmation token
Added confirmUser method to confirm user
Added ConfirmUser RequestHandler to confirm user
Added passmethods to have methods related to password and authentication
Changed confirm email to suit new procedure, the password is manually set by us and mailed to customer
Added show and hide code for preloader and download button for graph
Added convert current graph to downloadable PNG. And changes to suit new system in Chart.js

Added CDN versions of all scripts. Scripts are loaded in body. Hid range graph. Changed colors of overall graph cards to bluegray. Shifted overall graph sliders to respective cards. Removed 'From Event Start' option, renamed others for better understanding. Added pre-loader and download button.

Changed password encryption library to passlib. Added authentication to DashboardHandler. Converted normal dashboard rendering into method in genmethods. Added LoginHandler for login. ConfirmUser and LoginHandler to handlers, added cookie secret to app settings
